			Investment Banking		


Brian Barbosa 


			2017-03-09T13:44:35+00:00		





AboutBuy-Side Advisory Sell-Side Advisory Equity Sponsor Advisory & Financing Capital RaisingTeam










 





INVESTMENT BANKING 

Elevating the experience  


 






Bruderman Brothers, LLC is an independent, privately-owned investment bank that services a diverse array of clients. Our services include buy and sell-side advisory, equity sponsor advisory and financing, financial restructuring, and capital raising. We have expertise in a broad range of industries including healthcare, financial services, manufacturing, logistics, distribution, consumer goods, retail, and apparel. We are selective in the engagements we undertake. This ensures that our interests are aligned with those of our clients, and ultimately contributes to our very high success rate.
We are distinguished by an unrelenting commitment to our clients, and by complementary wealth management services that can assist clients both throughout and after the deal process, ensuring that the proceeds from their liquidity event are properly monitored and nurtured. As a multi-generational, boutique investment bank, Bruderman Brothers has built its reputation on uncompromising integrity and the involvement and dedication of senior management.






 
 

 
 
 
 



















