Home/Investment Banking/Buy-Side Advisory








			Buy-Side Advisory		


Brian Barbosa 


			2017-03-09T13:44:43+00:00		





AboutBuy-Side Advisory Sell-Side Advisory Equity Sponsor Advisory & Financing Capital RaisingTeam










 





INVESTMENT BANKING 

Elevating the experience  


 






Our buy-side advisory services help clients expand their businesses through acquisition. We find and evaluate potential acquisition targets, provide valuation analyses, and examine and propose financial and strategic alternatives. We also advise on timing, structure, financing, and the pricing of a proposed acquisition, as well as assist in the negotiation and closing of the transaction.
Our investment banking professionals are creative and innovative in structuring transactions and identifying viable sources of financing for corporate and private equity clients. We have experience raising capital to finance leveraged buyouts, acquisitions, recapitalizations, refinancing’s, management buyouts, and shareholder dividends. We also have public debt capital market capabilities, including underwriting and distribution services for investment-grade and high-yield debt offerings.






 
 

 
 
 
 



















Bruderman Brothers LLC and Bruderman Asset Management












































































 






















