Home/Investment Banking/Capital Raising








			Capital Raising		


Brian Barbosa 


			2017-03-07T03:28:04+00:00		





AboutBuy-Side Advisory Sell-Side Advisory Equity Sponsor Advisory & Financing Capital Raising Team










 





INVESTMENT BANKING 

Elevating the experience  


 






Our capital raising services arrange funding for working capital, growth initiatives, mergers and acquisitions, and corporate restructurings. We source equity capital from private equity funds, hedge funds, and high-net-worth individuals. Additionally, we have relationships with senior lenders and mezzanine funds that provide debt capital.






 
 

 
 
 
 



















Bruderman Brothers LLC and Bruderman Asset Management












































































 






















