History



A Legacy of Success

			Our family's investment management business has origins dating to the late 1800's, and for three 
			generations we have advised wealthy European investors, charitable and religious organizations, 
			and several royal families.
			

			Following nearly 100 years of advising wealthy and influential families, the logical progression 
			for our business was to provide investment banking services to the businesses owned by our 
			investment management clients.  Accordingly, in 1999, Bruderman Brothers was formed as a 
			broker-dealer registered with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission.
			

			Today, Bruderman Brothers specializes in providing investment banking services to closely-held 
			companies and family businesses.
			



