Merchant Banking




Cultivating Relationships and Long-Term Success

				Our merchant banking affiliate, Bruderman Enterprises, Inc., employs a broad investment 
				strategy and makes opportunistic investments across all asset classes and industries, 
				most recently in lower middle-market companies in the health care, consumer products and 
				services, and financial services industries. We form true partnerships and align our 
				interests with highly motivated, proven, and successful management teams.
				
 
				We invest in and acquire lower middle-market companies generating annual revenues 
				between $25 and $100 million. We may also invest alongside management and other equity 
				partners and can source any required acquisition financing.
				


