Team




Superior Talent and Steadfast Dedication
Bruderman Brothers' greatest asset is the commitment to excellence put forth by each employee on every engagement. Our team offers unique qualifications and skills that include superior merger, acquisition, and capital raising expertise, unparalleled access to resources, and superb execution quality. Unlike many of our competitors, our senior principals are accessible and extremely active in each stage of the transaction process. Each of the firm's employees and advisors personifies the qualities that separate Bruderman Brothers from its competitors.BrokerCheck® by FINRA
