AboutBuy-Side Advisory Sell-Side Advisory Equity Sponsor Advisory & Financing Capital RaisingTeam







 





INVESTMENT BANKING 

Elevating the experience  


 


Bruderman Brothers’ greatest asset is the commitment to excellence put forth by each employee on every engagement. Our team offers unique qualifications and skills that include superior merger, acquisition, and capital raising expertise, unparalleled access to resources, and superb execution quality. Unlike many of our competitors, our senior principals are accessible and extremely active in each stage of the transaction process. Each of the firm’s employees and advisors personifies the qualities that separate Bruderman Brothers from its competitors.
Our team is led by:
Matthew J. Bruderman ChairmanOliver Pursche Chief Executive OfficerGerard L. Eastman President of Investment BankingAndrew Klein Managing DirectorPaul E. Palmeri Managing DirectorRonald G. Lehman Managing DirectorGregory Taft Gerard Managing DirectorMatthew Hull Managing DirectorPetar Cokleski Senior AssociateJohn Palmeri  AnalystPeter Brandel Director of Business DevelopmentMatthew J. Bruderman
Chairman 

Matthew Bruderman leads all merchant and investment banking
activities for Bruderman Brothers, and takes great pride in
being personally involved in each transaction undertaken by
the firm. Matthew Bruderman has been active in financial services
for nearly 20 years, and represents the third generation of the
Bruderman family in the industry. Early in his career he held
positions in sales, investment and merchant banking, financial
planning, and investment management at T.R. Winston &
